#: admin/pages/views/partials/sections/section-ahsc-cron-status.php:13
#: admin/pages/views/partials/sections/section-ahsc-cron-status.php:17
msgid ""
"It allows you to schedule the automatic execution of some tasks, in specific "
"time intervals. By setting the execution frequency, all operations, such as "
"editing or publishing posts and pages, will be performed in the chosen "
"interval, possibly replacing the day and time scheduled on WordPress."
msgstr ""
"Permite programar la ejecución automática de ciertas tareas en intervalos de "
"tiempo específicos. Al establecer la frecuencia de ejecución, todas las "
"operaciones, como editar o publicar entradas y páginas, se realizarán en el "
"intervalo seleccionado, pudiendo reemplazar el día y la hora programados en "
"WordPress."

#: admin/pages/views/partials/sections/section-ahsc-static-cache.php:19
#: admin/pages/views/partials/sections/section-ahsc-static-cache.php:24
